22
00:01:19,126 --> 00:01:20,486
Why talk smack about him?

23
00:01:20,926 --> 00:01:21,926
What did you say?

24
00:01:23,126 --> 00:01:24,126
The one who saved us

25
00:01:25,286 --> 00:01:26,607
was Zhao Feiyang?

26
00:01:28,286 --> 00:01:29,327
Wasn't it Wang Hui?

27
00:01:30,247 --> 00:01:31,486
That hypocrite.

28
00:01:31,887 --> 00:01:32,887
No way he'd save us.

29
00:01:33,286 --> 00:01:34,566
