30
00:01:35,167 --> 00:01:36,286
It's true.

31
00:01:37,646 --> 00:01:38,766
I see.

32
00:01:39,286 --> 00:01:42,247
I must have taken two lotus seeds.

33
00:01:43,646 --> 00:01:44,807
He wasn't stingy

34
