35
00:01:48,006 --> 00:01:49,047
Then why did you say

36
00:01:51,687 --> 00:01:53,366
you didn't know who he was that day?

37
00:01:53,366 --> 00:01:55,327
♪Fleeting time passes through♪

38
00:01:55,327 --> 00:01:56,327
Okay, I admit it.

39
00:01:57,286 --> 00:01:58,286
I was being selfish

40
00:01:59,486 --> 00:02:00,486
