41
00:02:00,727 --> 00:02:02,406
Yanran, you...

42
00:02:18,486 --> 00:02:19,926
It's the Holy Lord!

43
00:02:20,567 --> 00:02:22,486
Greetings, Holy Lord!

44
00:02:22,646 --> 00:02:23,727
- Greetings, Holy Lord!
- Greetings, Holy Lord!

45
00:02:23,727 --> 00:02:24,966
Greetings, Holy Lord!

46
00:02:28,167 --> 00:02:29,167
Haotian Lord?

47
00:02:29,526 --> 00:02:30,526
How dare you!

48
00:02:30,966 --> 00:02:33,526
The entire Haotian Empire
belongs to my father.

49
00:02:33,766 --> 00:02:36,246
Why aren't you bowing to him?

50
00:02:36,407 --> 00:02:38,847
I intend to appoint you
as The Southern Domain Lord.

51
00:02:38,966 --> 00:02:40,806
What do you think?

52
00:02:40,887 --> 00:02:43,366
The Holy Lord wants to appoint Feiyang
as Domain Lord?

53
00:02:43,686 --> 00:02:44,206
Feiyang,

54
00:02:44,407 --> 00:02:46,086
hurry up and thank the Holy Lord!

55
00:02:46,287 --> 00:02:47,447
You'll be a Domain Lord.

56
00:02:47,766 --> 00:02:49,167
My son's going to be a Domain Lord!

57
00:02:50,727 --> 00:02:53,287
Our Zhao family's finally
hitting the big time!

58
00:02:54,926 --> 00:02:56,206
What's the catch

59
00:02:56,287 --> 00:02:58,086
to being this Domain Lord?

60
00:02:58,447 --> 00:02:59,447
Well.

61
00:02:59,887 --> 00:03:02,086
Just hand over that thunder power

62
00:03:02,366 --> 00:03:03,407
you got.

63
00:03:03,407 --> 00:03:04,486
Can't do that.

64
00:03:04,847 --> 00:03:05,887
This power

65
00:03:06,246 --> 00:03:07,766
exists within my consciousness.

66
00:03:08,206 --> 00:03:09,206
Stuck in my head.

67
00:03:09,447 --> 00:03:11,526
So, I'm going to have to pass on

68
00:03:11,806 --> 00:03:12,806
being the Domain Lord.

69
00:03:13,007 --> 00:03:14,007
Zhao Feiyang.

70
00:03:14,127 --> 00:03:15,966
This is a chance my dad is giving you!

71
00:03:16,366 --> 00:03:17,366
Don't blow it!

72
00:03:17,447 --> 00:03:18,607
What if I do blow it?

73
00:03:19,007 --> 00:03:21,127
As a Holy Lord of the Haotian Empire,

74
00:03:21,526 --> 00:03:23,206
you're sure quick to ask for my power.

75
00:03:23,486 --> 00:03:24,486
What is this?

76
00:03:25,007 --> 00:03:26,007
Robbery?

77
00:03:28,287 --> 00:03:29,766
Feiyang, that's the Holy Lord.

78
00:03:29,966 --> 00:03:30,966
Watch your mouth!

79
00:03:31,327 --> 00:03:32,327
Holy Lord.

80
00:03:32,686 --> 00:03:34,246
Please excuse my son's

81
00:03:34,246 --> 00:03:35,447
lack of manners.

82
00:03:35,567 --> 00:03:37,407
Jie said you'd no respect
for the royalty.

83
00:03:37,646 --> 00:03:39,127
I didn't believe him at first.

84
00:03:39,447 --> 00:03:41,646
But seeing it now, it's true.

85
00:03:42,287 --> 00:03:43,966
You're a pretty arrogant dude,

86
00:03:44,287 --> 00:03:46,007
showing no respect to me.

87
00:03:46,206 --> 00:03:47,607
I treat guests with respect,

88
00:03:48,206 --> 00:03:49,567
but wolves get weapons.

89
00:03:49,966 --> 00:03:51,086
My attitude depends on

90
00:03:51,727 --> 00:03:54,567
who I'm talking to.

91
00:03:55,086 --> 00:03:56,567
That's outrageous!

92
00:03:57,047 --> 00:03:59,366
My dad's a ninth-rank
Great Martial Saint!

93
00:03:59,526 --> 00:04:00,167
In the universe,

94
00:04:00,287 --> 00:04:02,246
only the Demon Lord

95
00:04:02,486 --> 00:04:04,206
can even compete.

96
00:04:04,447 --> 00:04:05,926
You're totally ungrateful!

97
00:04:06,047 --> 00:04:07,887
Father, don't waste more words on him.

98
00:04:08,007 --> 00:04:09,327
Just take away his thunder power.

99
00:04:09,567 --> 00:04:10,567
Remove this trouble.

100
00:04:10,686 --> 00:04:11,686
Zhao Feiyang.

101
00:04:12,086 --> 00:04:14,167
One last chance.

102
00:04:14,607 --> 00:04:15,607
If you don't cooperate,

103
00:04:15,887 --> 00:04:17,766
I will have to suppress you.

104
00:04:18,086 --> 00:04:20,086
Honestly, considering your merit,

105
00:04:20,766 --> 00:04:22,486
I don't want it to be like this.

106
00:04:29,806 --> 00:04:31,727
Feiyang, he's the Holy Lord.

107
00:04:32,087 --> 00:04:32,886
Whatever he wants,

108
00:04:32,967 --> 00:04:34,326
just give it to him.

109
00:04:35,207 --> 00:04:36,407
Even if it's my life,

110
00:04:37,366 --> 00:04:38,366
should I give it?

111
00:04:38,647 --> 00:04:39,647
Well...

112
00:04:42,366 --> 00:04:44,006
Is that your final answer?

113
00:04:44,087 --> 00:04:45,087
Yes.

114
00:04:45,207 --> 00:04:46,607
It is.

115
00:04:47,006 --> 00:04:48,006
But,

116
00:04:48,287 --> 00:04:50,407
I'll give you a chance too.

117
00:04:50,926 --> 00:04:52,087
If you leave now,

118
00:04:52,287 --> 00:04:52,926
I can pretend

119
00:04:52,926 --> 00:04:54,880
this never happened.

120
00:04:55,087 --> 00:04:56,326
Sounds like

121
00:04:57,167 --> 00:04:59,566
you want to test your strength
against me?

122
00:04:59,847 --> 00:05:00,847
No.

123
00:05:01,527 --> 00:05:02,527
You're just

124
00:05:03,727 --> 00:05:05,847
not a match for me.

125
00:05:06,686 --> 00:05:07,806
Are you out of your mind?

126
00:05:08,446 --> 00:05:09,246
Zhao Feiyang.

127
00:05:09,407 --> 00:05:11,287
My dad's a ninth-rank
Great Martial Saint!

128
00:05:11,446 --> 00:05:12,847
He might break to the tenth rank

129
00:05:12,967 --> 00:05:14,006
and become a god.

130
00:05:14,167 --> 00:05:15,926
You're saying he's no match?

131
00:05:17,886 --> 00:05:19,886
I know your thunder power

132
00:05:20,006 --> 00:05:21,047
is strong,

133
00:05:21,686 --> 00:05:23,287
but you don't have a Dantian.

134
00:05:23,527 --> 00:05:24,607
Just practicing Qi.

135
00:05:24,727 --> 00:05:25,847
How could you possibly

136
00:05:26,407 --> 00:05:27,727
develop this insane power

137
00:05:27,886 --> 00:05:29,527
with that kind of body?

138
00:05:30,767 --> 00:05:32,047
Who says I don't have a Dantian?

139
00:05:33,167 --> 00:05:34,847
And who says I'm just practicing Qi?

140
00:05:35,847 --> 00:05:36,847
Awesome!

141
00:05:36,847 --> 00:05:37,926
The Revolution Pill's done.

142
00:05:38,566 --> 00:05:40,607
Feiyang, you can restore your Dantian.

143
00:05:41,047 --> 00:05:42,047
Take it quick!

144
00:05:44,566 --> 00:05:46,047
But once I take it,

145
00:05:46,527 --> 00:05:48,607
my cultivation might skyrocket.

146
00:05:49,407 --> 00:05:50,566
I may even ascend right away.

147
00:05:51,767 --> 00:05:54,647
Isn't that the ultimate goal
for a practitioner?

148
00:05:55,207 --> 00:05:56,686
Is it okay if we can never

149
00:05:57,566 --> 00:05:58,566
see each other again?

150
00:06:00,407 --> 00:06:02,047
Hold the pill in your throat.

151
00:06:02,527 --> 00:06:04,486
Only take it
when you absolutely need to.

152
00:06:05,087 --> 00:06:06,566
When you ascend to godhood,

153
00:06:07,246 --> 00:06:09,207
