the Love Flower.

154
00:06:12,022 --> 00:06:15,639
♪East winds howl, snows persist,
sweet-bitter blend♪

155
00:06:15,767 --> 00:06:17,463
♪Heaven's will, Mortal ends♪

156
00:06:17,559 --> 00:06:19,287
♪Brushstrokes dance,
my joys and sorrows♪

157
00:06:19,287 --> 00:06:22,296
♪Moonlit toasts to love's remains♪

158
00:06:22,391 --> 00:06:25,033
♪Lifetimes ask, whose face sustains♪

159
00:06:25,033 --> 00:06:27,806
♪Rouge tears carving soul's chains♪

160
00:06:27,806 --> 00:06:28,806
Awesome, Young Master!

161
00:06:28,806 --> 00:06:32,847
♪Love falls faster than flames♪

162
00:06:32,847 --> 00:06:34,126
How is this even possible?

163
00:06:34,686 --> 00:06:35,686
He's just practicing Qi.

164
00:06:35,806 --> 00:06:37,126
How can he leap to the tenth rank

165
00:06:37,287 --> 00:06:38,366
and ascend to godhood?

166
00:06:38,527 --> 00:06:39,806
This defies the natural order!

167
00:06:40,607 --> 00:06:42,446
What I've stored
is the thunder tribulation.

168
00:06:43,167 --> 00:06:44,847
Even gods can barely
withstand its might.

169
00:06:45,047 --> 00:06:46,126
After acquiring a Dantian,

170
00:06:46,366 --> 00:06:48,246
I absorbed
all the thunder tribulation power.

171
00:06:48,527 --> 00:06:50,087
Defying the nature and become a god

172
00:06:50,287 --> 00:06:51,607
isn't really a surprise.

173
00:06:51,767 --> 00:06:54,047
Your thunder power is actually
the thunder tribulation!

174
00:06:54,047 --> 00:06:54,566
This...

175
00:06:55,008 --> 00:06:55,566
This...

176
00:06:55,566 --> 00:06:56,607
No way!

177
00:06:56,806 --> 00:06:58,686
You wanted this power, didn't you?

178
00:06:59,647 --> 00:07:01,207
Then I'll let you have a taste

179
00:07:01,486 --> 00:07:02,727
of the thunder tribulation.

180
00:07:05,607 --> 00:07:07,610
♪Blood-blossoms bloom♪

181
00:07:07,733 --> 00:07:10,389
♪Petals cling to madness' tune♪

182
00:07:10,464 --> 00:07:11,806
♪Cliffs echo with love's monsoon♪

183
00:07:11,806 --> 00:07:12,806
Oh my.

184
00:07:12,806 --> 00:07:15,087
♪Bound through death's marooned lagoon♪

185
00:07:15,087 --> 00:07:16,607
Mercy, Supreme God!

186
00:07:20,486 --> 00:07:21,047
Son,

187
00:07:21,366 --> 00:07:22,686
hold it right there!

188
00:07:22,886 --> 00:07:25,407
The Haotian Empire needs
the Holy Lord's protection.

189
00:07:25,527 --> 00:07:26,326
If you kill him,

190
00:07:26,527 --> 00:07:28,047
the Demon Lord will show up.

191
00:07:28,407 --> 00:07:30,686
It'll cause a catastrophe.

192
00:07:34,407 --> 00:07:35,407
Alright.

193
00:07:35,727 --> 00:07:36,926
Cultivation isn't easy.

194
00:07:37,126 --> 00:07:38,167
I'll spare your life.

195
00:07:39,207 --> 00:07:40,207
After I ascend,

196
00:07:40,928 --> 00:07:42,848
if you think about
coming after my Zhao family,

197
00:07:43,287 --> 00:07:44,806
or messing with my friends,

198
00:07:46,207 --> 00:07:49,366
I'll tear a hole in reality and wipe
your entire imperial family off the map.

199
00:07:49,967 --> 00:07:50,967
Got it?

200
00:07:51,967 --> 00:07:53,767
We understand, fully!

201
00:07:53,886 --> 00:07:55,087
Absolutely not.

202
00:07:55,407 --> 00:07:56,407
Never!

203
00:07:57,287 --> 00:07:58,287
Get lost!

204
00:08:04,551 --> 00:08:08,920
♪The wind howls, the sword unsheathes♪

205
00:08:10,975 --> 00:08:15,183
♪Unyielding to fate,
his resolve never fades♪

206
00:08:15,926 --> 00:08:16,926
My son.

207
00:08:17,006 --> 00:08:18,566
You've actually become an immortal?

208
00:08:18,727 --> 00:08:19,727
Right.

209
00:08:19,886 --> 00:08:20,886
I'm going to ascend.

210
00:08:21,967 --> 00:08:23,126
The Heaven's calling.

211
00:08:23,806 --> 00:08:24,806
Zhao Feiyang.

212
00:08:26,366 --> 00:08:27,366
What's going on?

213
00:08:29,126 --> 00:08:30,806
How are you standing in mid-air?

214
00:08:31,566 --> 00:08:32,566
You...

215
00:08:32,886 --> 00:08:34,087
you're at the tenth rank?

216
00:08:34,607 --> 00:08:35,647
Are you leaving?

217
00:08:36,806 --> 00:08:37,886
Are you over me?

218
00:08:38,926 --> 00:08:40,127
We haven't even...

219
00:08:41,407 --> 00:08:42,407
Sorry, guys.

220
00:08:43,047 --> 00:08:45,007
No much time to catch up.

221
00:08:45,407 --> 00:08:46,407
It's been great

222
00:08:46,686 --> 00:08:48,206
being with you all for so long.

223
00:08:48,806 --> 00:08:49,806
Guys,

224
00:08:50,007 --> 00:08:51,007
take care!

225
00:08:51,287 --> 00:08:53,247
I didn't want to make a scene,
considering

226
00:08:53,407 --> 00:08:54,407
our families' history.

227
00:08:54,647 --> 00:08:55,647
If you put it like that,

228
00:08:56,086 --> 00:08:57,167
then I, Chen Qiushui,

229
00:08:57,407 --> 00:08:59,086
am here to call off the engagement.

230
00:09:00,247 --> 00:09:01,566
(I just don't get it.)

231
00:09:02,726 --> 00:09:04,247
Why you have such a problem with me?

232
00:09:04,367 --> 00:09:06,086
Your actions disgust me.

233
00:09:06,206 --> 00:09:08,326
Bite me then!

234
00:09:08,326 --> 00:09:09,086
Zhao Feiyang,

235
00:09:09,247 --> 00:09:10,487
I swear I'll beat you up.

236
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:11,487
Wait.

237
00:09:11,487 --> 00:09:12,887
Don't cry.

238
00:09:13,767 --> 00:09:14,767
I'm sorry.

239
00:09:18,606 --> 00:09:19,806
(This is a Scarlet Fruit.)

240
00:09:19,806 --> 00:09:21,367
(A material for Revolution Pill.)

241
00:09:21,487 --> 00:09:22,566
(This...)

242
00:09:22,566 --> 00:09:24,407
(This is really too precious.)

243
00:09:24,566 --> 00:09:26,086
We're going to be a family.

244
00:09:27,846 --> 00:09:28,446
(Zhao Feiyang,)

245
00:09:28,846 --> 00:09:29,846
(will you)

246
00:09:30,527 --> 00:09:31,726
marry me?

247
00:09:32,167 --> 00:09:34,247
Our families have been friends
for generations.

248
00:09:35,007 --> 00:09:36,086
That's why we're engaged.

249
00:09:36,407 --> 00:09:38,287
We're engaged already.

250
00:09:38,686 --> 00:09:40,446
She's practically my fiancée.

251
00:09:40,566 --> 00:09:42,007
You think I'm out of line, or what?

252
00:09:42,127 --> 00:09:43,326
(I can't let your enemy)

253
00:09:43,446 --> 00:09:44,446
(walk away today.)

254
00:09:45,767 --> 00:09:47,446
(So I'll help you kill him)

255
00:09:48,007 --> 00:09:49,007
(as a betrothal gift.)

256
00:09:49,846 --> 00:09:50,966
(Are you serious?)

257
00:09:51,606 --> 00:09:52,606
Go for revenge.

258
00:09:54,007 --> 00:09:55,007
Kill him.

259
00:09:55,007 --> 00:09:56,767
You've been working for him
since little.

260
00:09:57,407 --> 00:09:58,527
Don't you know

261
00:09:58,686 --> 00:09:59,367
about him?

262
00:09:59,527 --> 00:10:00,367
But

263
00:10:00,527 --> 00:10:02,367
in my eyes, he is invincible.

264
00:10:02,566 --> 00:10:04,127
I want to get some candied hawthorns.

265
00:10:04,127 --> 00:10:05,127
Agreed.

266
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:07,241
♪He's unstoppable♪

267
00:10:07,726 --> 00:10:09,726
(You are indeed his good maid.)

268
00:10:09,926 --> 00:10:11,047
Awesome, Young Master!

269
00:10:14,336 --> 00:10:18,966
♪The brilliant galaxy lights my path♪

270
00:10:18,966 --> 00:10:19,566
Feiyang,

271
00:10:19,846 --> 00:10:20,887
you just left like this?

272
00:10:21,007 --> 00:10:21,632
You...

273
00:10:21,926 --> 00:10:23,527
My son!

274
00:10:24,407 --> 00:10:25,767
Feiyang!

275
00:10:27,072 --> 00:10:32,859
♪Leave a name in history,
praised for a thousand autumns♪

276
00:10:33,894 --> 00:10:38,838
♪Sung throughout the land,
respected by the world♪

277
00:10:39,114 --> 00:10:40,436
(To be continued. Stay tuned!)

278
